<title>Entie Hukdampa</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Entie, Hukdampa, na Lal chun,
 Thing hansie dawlah A hun ngak;
 Keile Hukdampa ei ngak-in.
 Ka hung hi, lam haksa mahleh.

[V2]
 Thepna lampi tincheng ale,
 Ka hun nungheisan loh na din;
 Van Angel lungtuok ginum te,
 Ka ngaihni hin hung tung sek leu.

[V3]
 2. En diu hinna ding lampi hi,
 Hawh ahak tun loh ka lau ie;
 Lalpa, van thagau puih loh chun,
 Kuo ahim a hungtung thei ding?

[V4]
 3. Bangtik leh ka hun mu ding um?
 Ka ngaklah lei dahum a hin;
 Nuoma ka len diu ka thil sek,
 Aw, nangmah hehpihna ziek hin.

[V5]
 4. Thing hansie dawl Kraws maktak chu,
 Lungngai taka ei tatna chu;
 &quot;Ka hinna pen thing kung ahi&quot;,
 Tiin chawisang zing thei leng aw.</lyrics>
</song>